<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>135</hymn_number>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
<title>yǔ zhǔ tóng qù 迦南135</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 yǔ zhǔ tóng qù, wǒ yào yǔ zhǔ tóng qù, méi yǒu liú liàn méi yǒu wǒ de zì jǐ,
 yǔ zhǔ tóng qù, wǒ yào yǔ zhǔ tóng qù, yǔ zhǔ hé ér wèi yī, zài yǐ
 hòu de suì yuè lǐ, wǒ yào zūn xíng shén de zhǐ yì,
 wú lùn tā ràng wǒ dào nà lǐ, wǒ de xīn zài shuō wǒ yào yǔ zhǔ tóng qù.</lyrics>
</song>